{"tid":887544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"血腥萬聖節　網美全裸爆乳噴血展銷魂之美","createTime":"2018-11-03T04:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T05:08:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c954e800d106d22787036d0a1976350110d3ea91","tid":887544,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"前日萬聖節，全世界各地都有不少活動炒熱萬聖節氣氛<br />\n泰國網美「Cup E」也拍攝一組以萬聖節為主題的照片<br />\n雖然充斥著暴力、血腥的氛圍，但也大展她的玲瓏有緻好身材。<br />\n <br />\n「Cup E」這次全裸進行拍攝，但身上灑了不少「血」與「吐血」更手持刀械，營造出暴力血腥美學。<br />\n「Cup E」說，這組照片是透過專業攝影師，在浴室裡進行拍攝但她也強調，這些照片都是經過特殊效果呈現<br />\n呼籲網友與粉絲不要「信以為真」並模仿，並告誡網友們「來真的」會非常危險。<br />\n <br />\n不少網友看過這組圖片後，紛紛讚許「Cup E」：「很性感，但也很恐怖。」「嚇到我了！」、「萬聖節快樂！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/grgfRFd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgrgfRFd.png&h=bbf80ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yT6C40f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyT6C40f.png&h=483a0a82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFWPbFg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFWPbFg.png&h=afdc7a31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5426Ykh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5426Ykh.png&h=60623197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdHR9rZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdHR9rZ.png&h=a23712cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gB4pK0k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgB4pK0k.png&h=3005622f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"074b0366d965d1220bf339e7e441804e892224c1","tid":887544,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"紋身雞"},{"pid":"c340450484803c93c267d56194fb1372ec8f495c","tid":887544,"uid":68851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal